description:
This is a 37 minute workout called '35 MIN CARDIO PILATES || At-Home Full Body Workout' from the channel Move With Nicole.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.
